WEBVTT

00:06:58.810 --> 00:07:02.527
Hany is one of 50 million people

00:07:02.527 --> 00:07:06.105
uprooted in this world today.

00:07:06.105 --> 00:07:08.884
Never since World War II

00:07:08.884 --> 00:07:14.151
have so many people been forcibly displaced.

00:07:14.151 --> 00:07:16.780
So while we're making sweeping progress

00:07:16.780 --> 00:07:18.881
in human health,

00:07:18.881 --> 00:07:23.875
in technology, in education and design,

00:07:23.875 --> 00:07:27.238
we are doing dangerously little

00:07:27.238 --> 00:07:30.546
to help the victims